##Pivgeon-proxy

This application accepts emails notifications from SendGrid and relays requests to our fork of BookOrder: https://github.com/oxos/book-order-pivgeon

Yes, this simple service consists of two apps. You can check out older version that created stories directly using Pivotal Tracker API: https://github.com/oxos/pivgeon-proxy/tree/57c144da4cf88812c4057ec4f0051d94ebb81b10
or head directly to https://github.com/nwp/book-order.